# git-commit-watch repo list — one absolute (or ~-prefixed) path per line.
# Blank lines and # comments are ignored.
# Copy this file to git-commit-watch.list (which is gitignored) to activate.
#
# Example entries:
# ~/Projects/obsidian-mcp-server
# ~/Projects/claude-chat-bridge
# ~/Projects/obsidian-claude-plugin
